OK, so that was part one.

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:43.539
That's just, you know, why I'm
here-- bite-sized cupcakes.

00:08:43.539 --> 00:08:45.860
They're really amazing.

00:08:45.860 --> 00:08:47.610
I could ice cupcakes
all day long.

00:08:47.610 --> 00:08:48.850
I used to.

